16 WHEREAS, throughout its history, Caterpillar Inc. has remained dedicated to its core values
17 of integrity, teamwork, and sustainability, fostering a culture of continuous improvement,
18 responsible business practices, and environmental stewardship; and
19 WHEREAS, as Caterpillar Inc. embarks on its next century, it remains committed to
20 advancing technology, driving sustainable solutions, and supporting communities through
21 economic investment and philanthropic initiatives; and
22 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this extraordinary company, which has
23 played an integral role in shaping industries and communities for a century, be appropriately
24 honored during this special time.
25 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
26 the members of this body congratulate Caterpillar Inc. upon the grand occasion of its 100th
27 anniversary, commend its exemplary industry achievements and contributions, and extend
28 best wishes for its continued success.
29 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
30 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
31 Caterpillar Inc.
